y":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T08:40:16.000Z","msg":"後悔冇賣理hazard"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T08:45:49.000Z","msg":"你估佢唔想賣咩 連連失分個時已經係咁怨夏薩特傷咁耐都唔出 <br />\n不過自己早一步比人炒左咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"241f211669bdab69b530c82409c760ce2e172f5d","tid":708274,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T08:47:32.000Z","msg":"渣古同迪布尼幾多個英超牙"},{"pid":"d8233d74705886137d53f3e3e86be7f6e1933a04","tid":708274,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T08:48:58.000Z","msg":"熱身賽踢到屎咁唔見死出黎... 上半場又好好咩"},{"pid":"bf79de635ef57bbbc22f54f6013b7361d6d5973c","tid":708274,"uid":144466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T08:52:11.000Z","msg":"贏巴拿馬都打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f282eb28ddd94ce8724a503c5521aac3d521579","tid":708274,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T08:52:32.000Z","msg":"父親節快樂 daddy😘😘😘"},{"pid":"3616e260795cec85f32b870fa5d1bec5b662a0fc","tid":708274,"uid":14652,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T08:57:29.000Z","msg":"明明係靠梅頓斯<br />\n賽後焦點去哂佢地三個到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c563fd51ea592343d75680767d2f7a8ccd656b","tid":708274,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T08:58:34.000Z","msg":"對住巴拿馬都好j<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5cb4bd79ecf514cc1079823a18bea2692d312c","tid":708274,"uid":142314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T09:10:00.000Z","msg":"化學作用0 都可以吹成千幾字"},{"pid":"298f3e56af119482353581a8017f3ad80ae53257","tid":708274,"uid":82720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T09:13:06.000Z","msg":"後悔無買梅頓斯"},{"pid":"0732b1bfe20efd311eaf85af38e166c004d209a9","tid":708274,"uid":87072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d823